API Documentation. (GET is the default method)

FifaApi:

/fifa-api/status/
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/week-user/
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/week-distr/ [POST the filter] 
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/week-distr/filter
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/week-distr/result
/fifa-api/statistics/matchdistribution/week-distr/goals

/users/active/usernames
/users/ [optional param: active (boolean). return active players only]
/statistics/player/ [required params: username and TimeRangeAggr (MONHT, WEEK)]
/statistics/opponents/ [return list of challengeReport for that challenge between two users. Required params: opponent1 and opponent2 and timerangeaggr]
/statistics/opponents/generalstats/ [required param: opponent1 and opponent2 as usernames]

/fifa-api/matches/ [possible params: username, email of player, id of the match, limit as nuumber of matches. 
The call returns an array of matches. If nothing is specified all matches are returned]

/fifa-api/matches/random/withcomments
/fifa-api/matches/random/withcomments/simpleformat
/fifa-api/matches/size [username as param, query string]

/fifa-api/general-stats/ [possible params: username or email of player]

FuelApi:


/fuel/20112017/ [POST the refueling]
/fuel/month/price/
/fuel/month/distance/
/fuel/month/distance-quantity/
